Decision Optimization (Beta)

After a model is deployed to Salesforce, Einstein Discovery can use it to get predicted outcomes and suggested improvements. You can display predictions in Lightning record pages and Experience Cloud sites pages. You can also get predictions programmatically using the Einstein Prediction Service via REST or Apex API calls.

Automated Prediction Writeback
Use a special prediction field to save prediction scores directly on records.
On-Demand Predictions
Initiate predictions through various interfaces, including Einstein Discovery in Tableau.
Predictions in Data Prep
Bake predictions into your CRM Analytics datasets with recipes and dataflows.
